milestones.description: Imran Khan and Shahid Mahboob's 144-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Imran Khan and Wasim Raja
Roy Dias has broken the record for most catches (7) in ODIs for SL, going past Duleep Mendis's 6
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (22) for SL, going past Duleep Mendis
Imran Khan and Shahid Mahboob's 144-run partnership is the highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 130 between Bevan Congdon and Ken Wadsworth
